 people shall use it as a reference book and mnemonic aid. I will describe the 18 most important plants that every master of herbology and in the first place every cleric shall know who is willing to ensure the grace of Gods by using the traditional rituals.§($1,>) §§Aldaka\n\nAldaka is the name of a mushroom. It´s characteristical colour is grey, which has been known to even have a silvery sheen in somespecimen. The Aldaka-mushroom has a regular round hood and a short and thick stem. It favours paltry ground, like it is found onthe rolling hills of Elerion. If one is looking for this mushroom, one should look for big rocks, because it grows mostly on thedownwind side. The ritualistic use of Aldaka makes use of the entire mushroom. It has to be dried out in the open air and thenbe made into a fine powder through the use of an mortar and pestle. Prepared like this, the powder can be used to get the mercyof the God of Animal Husbandry. This makes it possible to boost the production of\
 animal resources for a short time.§($2,<,-1) §§
